```

**Typosquatting:**
```
http://paypa1.com/secure/login
http://g00gle.com/verify
```

**Clean URL:**
```
https://github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-python
```

## Features

- **Upload files**: .eml, .pdf, .docx, .txt, images
- **Paste URLs**: Direct analysis in chat
- **OCR**: Extract text from screenshots
- **Email auth**: SPF/DKIM/DMARC verification
- **Threat intel**: VirusTotal integration

